description:
This is a 26 minute workout called '25 MIN STRONG YOGA & STRETCH - Full Body, Low Impact Home Workout - No Equipment, No Repeats' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Try this new STRONG YOGA inspired stretch routine to help you increase your mobility and flexibility. I hope you enjoy doing regular mobility sessions and feel super relaxed at the end of this one. No expectations, just follow along! Remember: your body deserves some extra love on your rest days ❤️
